
### `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python build
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.so
*.egg-info/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
env/
venv/
ENV/
.venv.bak/

# macOS system files
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# Editor settings
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# Logs and dumps
*.log
memory_log.txt
memory_log.csv
system_monitor.log
*.bak
*.pid
*.out

# Snapshots or auto-generated assets
snapshots/
*.json

# Secrets and keys
*.key
*.pem
*.p12

# Optional GUI temp/cache
.cache/
__snapshots__/
.qgis2/

# Test outputs
.pytest_cache/
htmlcov/
coverage.xml

# Exclude platform-specific outputs
*.dSYM/
*.lprof